html.htmlText:
We would like to invite you in our luxury one bedroom apartment in the center of Prague with a magnificent river view.

Ideal for families or business trip is located right next to the river Vltava. This luxury fully equipped apartment includes an amazing spacious living room together with cozy dining area, beautiful and stylish bedroom, fully equipped kitchen and modern bathroom.

You are welcome in our unique apartment, it will be our pleasure to host you!

The apartment is located in a historical building with elevator which is between the floors and starts from the upper ground floor + few steps, the apartment is on the top floor. It includes fully equipped kitchen, full modern bathroom, luxury bedroom with king bed, and a cozy living room including dinning area. The apartment is covered with excellent WIFI internet, professional portable air-condition in living room and portable fan in the bedroom. Also there is a wide balcony with access from the living room and bedroom too. Everything needed for an enjoyable stay in Prague
Before the arrival of the guest the apartment will always be prepared and clean, all that is written and what you see on the pictures can be used for your comfortable stay

- late check in - free of charge

- city tax - 50czk for person per night

- cleaning fee - free of charge (it is included in the price)

- We can arrange taxi transport from/to the airport - 800 czk in one way or 1500 czk in both ways, from/to the bus or train station 350 czech crowns in one way. Important note: - the prices are up to 4 guests and maximum 3 bags (luggage), otherwise we will need to send two cab

- We can recommend for our guests sightseeing tours, best restaurants and places to visit. Also we can arrange some tours and dinner in our favorite restaurants

- Keys delivery upon arrival - we will meet personally at the address of the apartment

html.htmlText: We would like to kindly ask you to pay attention to the most important regarding the house rules: - Smoking is not allowed (there is alarm) - Number of guests allowed to stay in the apartment - only the guests stated in the reservation, otherwise the host has the full right to cancel the accommodation for all guests; - Any kind of parties and visits are not allowed at all, it is strictly forbidden - Quiet hours after 22h (please respect the neighbors) - Please do not re-arrange the furniture; - Please do not damage towels and sheets and please do your best to leave them without stains; - Maintain a good level of cleanliness in the kitchen and wash all dirty dishes, glasses or any kitchen utensils you used during your stay and do not leave any food or drinks inside the fridge on the check out; - Please take all of the trash into the recycle bins of the building; - In case of any accidental damage, please inform us in time and we’ll look into the issue together to find the best solution for all; Maximum respect of the written above will be highly and sincerely appreciated

localizedReview.comments: Thank you for the wonderful apartment, high quality accommodation! We wish you grateful customers and prosperity! you are SUPER!🤗

reviews.comments:
¡Una experiencia excepcional!
Este apartamento superó todas mis expectativas. Desde el momento en que llegamos, la limpieza y el orden fueron evidentes, lo cual me dio una gran sensación de confort. La comodidad es insuperable; el espacio es perfecto para toda la familia. Mis hijos se sintieron increíblemente a gusto y disfrutaron de cada rincón del lugar. Además, la comunicación con el anfitrión fue fluida, amable y siempre dispuesta a resolver cualquier duda o solicitud. Definitivamente, es el mejor lugar en el que me he hospedado en mucho tiempo. ¡Lo recomiendo 100%! Sin duda volvería.

localizedReview.comments:
Exceptional experience!
This apartment exceeded all of my expectations. From the moment we arrived, the cleanliness and order were evident, which gave me a great feeling of comfort. Comfort is second to none; the space is perfect for the whole family. My children felt incredibly at ease and enjoyed every corner of the place. In addition, communication with the host was smooth, friendly, and always ready to answer any questions or requests. It's definitely the best place I've stayed in a long time. I recommend it 100%! I would definitely go back.
